Package: phira-mp-plus-server
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, adduser
Description: Real-time multiplayer game server for Phira+
 Phira-mp+ (PMP) is the real-time multiplayer game runtime for the Phira+
 architecture. It handles TCP game protocol, session management, room state
 machines, game rounds, trusted WASM plugin execution, and reliable event
 persistence.
 .
 PMP operates on a trusted internal network behind Phira+ Backend (PPB).
 It is not a public-facing web gateway.
